<div class="jumbotron">
  <p class="text-primary" style="font-size:400%"><strong>To-do</strong></p>
    <p class="lead text-primary"><em>To-do helps you keep track of your tasks!</em></p>
    <% if !current_user%>
      <p class="text-primary">
        <%= link_to "Sign In", new_user_session_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %> or
        <%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %> today!
      </p>
    <% end %>
</div>

<div class="row">
  
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <h2>User friendly</h2>
    <p>To-do is easy to do. Just sign up, confirm your email and start keeping track of your to-do items!</p>
  </div>

  <div class="col-md-6">
    <h2>Keeps you motivated</h2>
    <p>To-do keeps you on track by setting expiration dates on your task. If God created the world in 7 days, why shouldn't you be able to clear your little items in the same time?</p>
  </div>

</div>